---
import HeroImage from '../../assets/dimma.jpg';
---

<section
	class="gradient sm:min-h-[33em] min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center"
>
	<div class="space-y-7 sm:max-w-lg sm:px-0 max-w-[80%]">
		<p class="text-sm">Hello my name is</p>
		<div class="flex sm:flex-row flex-col sm:items-center gap-5">
			<img
				src={HeroImage}
				alt="Chidimma Ozomma Linda"
				class="sm:h-40 h-[300px] sm:w-40 rounded-xl aspect-square object-cover"
			/>
			<h1
				class="sm:stext-5xl text-4xl max-[361px]:text-3xl font-bold lh-12"
			>
				Chidimma <br class="hidden sm:block" />Ozomma
			</h1>
		</div>
		<p class="text-[15px] leading-6">
			I'm a frontend developer with a good knowledge of html and css, I'm
			currently on track to become a fullstack developer with the zuri
			internship
		</p>
	</div>
</section>
